events.comment:
if enemy center x position is less than player center x position (means the enemy is on the left side of the player)
and the enemy is flipped,
then we dont flip the enemy

if enemy center x position is greater than player center x position (means the enemy is on the right side of the player)
and the enemy is not flipped,
then we flip the enemy

if this is the last attacked enemy (variable is true)
and the healthbar is not visible
then we show both the enemy healthbar, and the profile picture
